    "content": "<ComponentCodePreview name=\"spotlight-card-demo\" />\n\n## Installation\n\n<Tabs defaultValue=\"cli\">\n\n<TabsList>\n  <TabsTrigger value=\"cli\">CLI</TabsTrigger>\n  <TabsTrigger value=\"manual\">Manual</TabsTrigger>\n</TabsList>\n<TabsContent value=\"cli\">\n\n```bash\nnpx shadcn@latest add \"https://smooth-ui/r/spotlight-card\"\n```\n\n</TabsContent>\n\n<TabsContent value=\"manual\">\n\n<Steps>\n\n<Step>Copy and paste the following code into your project.</Step>\n\n<ComponentSource name=\"spotlight-card\" />\n\n<Step>Update the import paths to match your project setup.</Step>\n\n</Steps>\n\n</TabsContent>\n\n</Tabs>\n\n## Examples\n\n### Custom Color\n<ComponentCodePreview name=\"spotlight-custom-color\" className=\"mb-6\" />\n\n### Dynamically colored border\n<ComponentCodePreview name=\"spotlight-card-border\" className=\"mb-6\" />\n\n### Overlay highlight\n<ComponentCodePreview name=\"spotlight-card-highlight\" className=\"mb-4\" />\n\n## Props\n### Spotlight Card\n               \n| Name               | Default                   | Description                                              \n| ------------------ | ------------------------- | -------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------\n| **as**             | **div**                   | **React.ElementType**<div>The element type to render the component as (e.g., `div`, `button`, `section`)</div>                  \n| **className**      | **—**                     | **String**<div>The class name of the spotlight component.</div>\n| **size**           | **100**                   | **Number**<div>Gradient size</div>\n| **from**           | **rgba(255,255,255,0.4)** | **String**<div>Starting color stop</div>\n| **via**            | **—**                     | **String**<div>Middle color stop</div>\n| **to**             | **transparent**           | **String**<div>Ending color stop</div>\n| **opacity**        | **100**                   | **Number**<div>opacity of the effect</div>\n| **isAround**       | **false**                 | **Boolean**<div>Whether the spotlight is surrounded by a background</div>\n| **mode**           | **before**                | **before \\| aflter**<div>Highlight display mode</div>",
